OL,3,CScrap bedroom tax at October Budget,
OL,4,CSNP urges Chancellor
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves has been
OL,7,Furged to scrap the so-called bedroom
OL,8,Ftax at this month's Budget.
OL,10,FThe SNP has pushed the Government to
OL,11,Fmove on the issue, which sees cash
OL,12,Fdeducted from benefits if the
OL,13,Frecipient has a spare room in their
OL,14,Fhome.
OL,16,FThe Scottish Government has attempted
OL,17,Fto mitigate the impacts of the
OL,18,Finitiative north of the border in
OL,19,Frecent years through discretionary
OL,20,Fhousing payments (DHPs).
