OL,3,CScrap bedroom tax at October Budget,
OL,4,CSNP urges Chancellor
OL,6,FResearch from the House of Commons
OL,7,FLibrary, commissioned by the SNP,
OL,8,Fshows that just shy of 100,000
OL,9,Fhouseholds in Scotland are impacted by
OL,10,Fthe bedroom tax.
OL,12,FThe research also found that #81.8
OL,13,Fmillion was deducted from the benefits
OL,14,Fof Scots in 2023-24, while the
OL,15,FGovernment spent #70.4 million on
OL,16,Fmitigation of the policy and #84.9
OL,17,Fmillion on DHPs as a whole.
