OL,3,CScrap bedroom tax at October Budget,
OL,4,CSNP urges Chancellor
OL,6,FSNP deputy Westminster leader Pete
OL,7,FWishart said: "Thousands of low-income
OL,8,Ffamilies across Scotland and the UK
OL,9,Fare being pushed into poverty by
OL,10,Fpunitive Labour Government policies
OL,11,Flike the bedroom tax.
OL,13,F"Voters in Scotland were promised
OL,14,Fchange but so far all they have seen
OL,15,Fis Labour Government ministers lining
OL,16,Ftheir own pockets with more than
OL,17,F#800,000 of freebies, while imposing
OL,18,Fpainful austerity cuts on the rest of
OL,19,Fus.
