OL,3,CScrap bedroom tax at October Budget,
OL,4,CSNP urges Chancellor
OL,6,F"It's not a good look that the
OL,7,FChancellor seems to be more interested
OL,8,Fin bagging designer clothes for
OL,9,Fherself than tackling poverty.
OL,11,F"She must use the UK Budget for a
OL,12,Ftotal reset, including by abolishing
OL,13,Fthe bedroom tax without further delay.
OL,15,F"This is a cruel policy that punishes
OL,16,Fthe poorest households simply for
OL,17,Fliving in their family homes ` and it
OL,18,Fdisproportionately affects Scotland.
