OL,3,CScrap bedroom tax at October Budget,
OL,4,CSNP urges Chancellor
OL,6,F"It's shameful that the Labour
OL,7,FGovernment made the political choice
OL,8,Fto keep it in place.
OL,10,F"Politics is about priorities ` the
OL,11,FSNP government is spending hundreds of
OL,12,Fmillions tackling poverty and cleaning
OL,13,Fup the mess that successive Labour and
OL,14,FTory UK governments have imposed on
OL,15,FScotland.
OL,17,F"If the Chancellor fails to act, the
OL,18,FLabour Government will push even more
OL,19,Ffamilies into poverty and cost
OL,20,FScotland millions of pounds every
OL,21,Fyear."
